text: Hannes Björninen (born 19 October 1995) is a Finnish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Lahti Pelicans in the Finnish Liiga. Björninen made his Liiga debut playing with Lahti Pelicans during the 2014–15 season. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish ice hockey forwards Category:Lahti Pelicans players
